<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Ashes" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Ashes,</orth> 1) the remains of any thing burnt: <bibl n="shak. son 73.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 73, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.1.345" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 1, 345</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.3.9" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 3, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.190" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 1, 190</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.92" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.3.7" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 3, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.174" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 174</bibl>. <cit><quote>repentant a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 4.1.111" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 1, 111</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>mourn in a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 5.1.49" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 1, 49</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>repent in a. and sackcloth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.221" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 221</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>pale as a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 3.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 2, 55</bibl></cit>. <emph>the roses in thy cheeks shall fade to paly a.</emph> (== to ashy paleness) <bibl n="shak. rom 4.1.100" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 1, 100</bibl>.<lb />2) the remains of the human body: <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.6.24" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 6, 24</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.6" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 4.2.75" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 IV, 2, 75</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 4.2.75" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 IV, 2, 75</bibl>. <cit><quote>of shame's a. shall my fame be bred,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1188" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1188</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.7.92" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 7, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.4.35" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 4, 35</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.5.42" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 5, 42</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>